      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This car has character and is ready for a new owner who doesn't mind rolling up their sleeves! While it shows significant wear and tear and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own this model at a fraction of the usual cost. Perfect for a mechanic's special or someone looking for a fixer-upper with potential!",
