      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and requires significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has a major oil leak and a persistent knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door, while the interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery and a non-functional infotainment system. This would be a suitable project car for a mechanic or a source for parts.",
