      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and entirely free from rock chips, swirls, or any surface imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no signs of bolster wear, and the interior is strictly smoke-free and pet-free. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions perfectly, and the carpets have been protected by custom mats since the car was new. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of every service record included. It has been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
